[Student "S"]
{There is only one reason that EAST should not overcall with 1\S. He is too strong. 
The maximum strength of an overcall is 16 points. Above that you should double.

So EAST doubles, and after WEST bids 2\C, EAST bids 2\S. This shows an overcall 
type hand, but with 17 or more points.

WEST has fine trump support and 8 points so she bids a confident 4\S.}

